{"tid":2498691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何漢權特首選委　台大畢業　有民國身分證　如未註銷或犯台國安法","createTime":"2021-04-21T10:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T11:40:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"92daaa3bb127eabf3dc03359f88eb6fa13b13c77","tid":2498691,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10160793778252678&amp;id=631862677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10160793778252678%26id%3D631862677&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=353aed53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10160793778252678&amp;id=631862677</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTFyXdaZo3JqEtenUjMiVWPyjApLj7dqYX7msVaocH6Nx?filename=URtr0rE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURtr0rE.jpg&h=c9196749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者：張三志榮<br />\n<br />\n右下何漢權台大歷史系畢業，有中華民國國民身分證，未知有否申請註銷。<br />\n如未註銷國民身分證，有否違犯中華民國國安法？"},{"pid":"357f59183032bf3ff5869dfed32047e417a6f387","tid":2498691,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"擔心佢"},{"pid":"bd5ba5f2e95b2a1697dc026dbbc17314fba24748","tid":2498691,"uid":358233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"台灣係中國一部分，都係中國人，不用分太細！"},{"pid":"95fe7889eb73c6b9b77f7ecd45742c3e998de6ff","tid":2498691,"uid":3801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"點樣去台灣舉報佢？"},{"pid":"749144f9f1440d1b69d98f2f3666e0061b65fae4","tid":2498691,"uid":54841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"舉報共匪 人人有責"},{"pid":"7c183c270b590a4e559763b4a5e11d78f3c9099b","tid":2498691,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要關注"},{"pid":"7ece195501bf9cc3cee0ac3c48ad3e6ca7f39abf","tid":2498691,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"台獨分子何漢權"},{"pid":"0b3a87ba88a1650a473383e09d54b8d4bcad662d","tid":2498691,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:26:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mjib.gov.tw/EditPage/?PageID=add74f0d-3b86-4f04-bdb5-092deb465f7d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mjib.gov.tw%2FEditPage%2F%3FPageID%3Dadd74f0d-3b86-4f04-bdb5-092deb465f7d&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=29acefdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mjib.gov.tw/EditPage/?PageID=add74f0d-3b86-4f04-bdb5-092deb465f7d</a><br />\n<br />\n電話、親自、信函、線上檢舉說明<br />\n調查局 為民服務 陳情檢舉管道 電話、親自、信函、線上檢舉說明<br />\n電話、親自、信函、線上檢舉說明 線上陳情檢舉信箱 陳情檢舉處理流程說明<br />\n<br />\n為確實保障民眾之權益，鼓勵民眾踴躍檢舉不法，本局針對職掌及階段性任務接受陳情 （檢舉）之方式為：<br />\n<br />\n電話檢舉：<br />\n在局本部及各外勤單位均設置專線檢舉電話，並派有專任調查人員接談處理。 <br />\n <br />\n親自檢舉：<br />\n民眾親自至局本部或各外勤單位檢舉陳情，均有專任調查人員接談處理。 <br />\n <br />\n信函檢舉：<br />\n在各縣市設置專用檢舉信箱，檢舉函件屬本局職掌範圍者由本局處理，否則酌視內容函轉權責機關參處；函復檢還理由或提供參考建議。<br />\n <br />\n線上檢舉：<br />\n利用本網站所附之電子檢舉信箱，投訴檢舉信函。"},{"pid":"797e6f370f8a03dd5ec0db09e2061ab49443ec57","tid":2498691,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"何漢權藍到黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9ac264b3ce7733caf7ca6477b0998d5b0bfdbe","tid":2498691,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"向台灣安全部門報告"},{"pid":"8c4e44f04018389c1249a6abb323041c5ae62358","tid":2498691,"uid":39092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd5ba5f2e95b2a1697dc026dbbc17314fba24748","tid":2498691,"uid":358233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"台灣係中國一部分，都係中國人，不用分太細！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"台灣係中國一部分<br />\n何漢權違反台灣國安法<br />\n咁何漢權係咪即係違反左國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}